## GSD planning (gsd-docs)

This workspace uses `gsd-docs/` for centralized GSD planning. The `.planning/`
directory at the workspace root is a symlink into `gsd-docs/`. Shared project
context (PROJECT.md, codebase intel) lives in `gsd-docs/projects/{{ ade_name }}/`;
personal implementation plans live in `gsd-docs/users/<handle>/projects/{{ ade_name }}/.planning/`.

- Push planning changes to `gsd-docs` on the `docs` branch only.
- Push code changes per-repo as usual.
- Use `gsd-docs/bin/gsd-split-commit` for combined flows.
- Never modify files under `gsd-docs/users/<someone-else>/`.

See `gsd-docs/README.md` and `gsd-docs/LAYOUT.md` for the full specification.

